Loved it! Totally unique independent video. The host Big D travels to Amsterdam, Belgium, Germany, and Prague. These Red Light Districts are amazing! It's hard to believe that the working women stand behind storefront windows in Europe. It's basically like a video guide to the Red Light Districts of Europe. I had a lot of fun watching this video. The cathouse in Prague was totally cool, as was the Sauna Club in Germany. I'm already planning my trip! LOL!

The DVD was just a compilation of "Big D" haging out in Europe. Little to no concrete information or advice is given. It's also fairly tame concerning nudity or sex. The Prague section is best and the most informative.
